{{Quote|&hellip; to my fellow grand moffs, and to the grand admirals, other officers, stormtroopers, bounty hunters, slavelords, and slaves, I bid you all Dark Greetings!|[[Bertroff Hissa]] at the Committee's opening|<ref name="The Glove of Darth Vader">''[[The Glove of Darth Vader]]''</ref>}}
The '''Central Committee of Grand Moffs''' was a collective body of [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moffs]] within the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. In [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the majority of the Grand [[Moff/Legends|Moffs]] attempted to subvert [[Ysanne Isard]]'s claim to rule the Empire.

Disregarding the authority of the weakened [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Imperial Ruling Council]], it instead formed an alliance with the [[Warlord/Legends|warlord]] [[Trioculus]] and his [[Trioculus' Empire|faction]]. [[Bertroff Hissa]] was its organizer and unspoken leader, and moffs [[Vilim Disra]], [[Dunhausen]], [[Muzzer]], and [[Thistleborn]] were senior members of its Council. The face of its operations, Trioculus, was a weak figurehead championed as the mutant son of [[Palpatine/Legends|the late Emperor]], and was ostensibly the committee's head. They were stationed aboard the [[Moffship]].

The committee organized the assassination of [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Rufaan Tigellinus]], and met on [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]] to advance Trioculus's claim to the Imperial throne. After the deaths of its founder and figurehead, any and all future plans to subdue the Alliance by said committee were discontinued.

